  "title": "Nyf's Genetics",
  "description": "Genetically Modify Minecraft Mobs!",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/880211352751329322/1166410524385345556/image.png?ex=654a6373&amp;is=6537ee73&amp;hm=4983d3c4a37e3ea4a5132fb4b66aa69e91fddca46aedc17301d627da43348344&amp;=&amp;width=1440&amp;height=174\" width=\"1200\" height=\"136\" /></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Nyf's Genetics is a mod that adds Genetics to Vanilla Mobs!</h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />Currently only adds Genetics to Villagers(More in future Updates).</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">There are currently 7 Traits for Villagers, each trait has 3 or more options, 3 base options and 1 or more Mutation Options.<br />Mutation Options are only obtainable via Breeding.<br />Breeding uses a punnett square setup with a chance for mutations.</p>\n<div>\n<p><img style=\"float: left;\" src=\"https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/977009237861498990/1166036392019755099/image.png?ex=65490703&amp;is=65369203&amp;hm=f2f9a14a33d7f3772c6215c43eb2a4e282928a60a4fc0b2b95dcf55a23720fd7&amp;=&amp;width=335&amp;height=671\" alt=\"\" width=\"100\" height=\"200\" /></p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\">Traits:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Eyebrow Type</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;Eye Color</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;Hair Type</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;Hair Color</li>\n<li>&nbsp;Height</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;Nose Size</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;Skin Tone</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
